            Bureau of Economic Analysis

            Methodologies

   Descriptions of the methodologies used to prepare BEA's national,
   industry, regional, and international programs are accessible on this
   page.

     Note:
      These methodologies are periodically refined to incorporate new and
     better source data and improved estimating procedures. The
     refinements are described in articles in BEA's monthly SURVEY OF
     CURRENT BUSINESS that present annual or comprehensive revisions to
     the estimates.

